2023
01:42:14,294 --> 01:42:15,886
"You're full of shit! "

2024
01:42:16,096 --> 01:42:17,120
Hear that?

2025
01:42:18,265 --> 01:42:19,857
He said we're full of shit.

2026
01:42:22,035 --> 01:42:23,024
Wait.

2027
01:42:26,874 --> 01:42:28,068
