2052
01:43:10,417 --> 01:43:11,406
What's that?

2053
01:43:11,618 --> 01:43:13,449
A governor's silver umbrella.

2054
01:43:13,654 --> 01:43:14,814
Take it!

2055
01:43:15,155 --> 01:43:16,918
- Which way to Shanxi?
- I have four more.

2056
