I know the way.

2057
01:43:18,559 --> 01:43:19,617
Will you spare me if I tell you?

2058
01:43:19,826 --> 01:43:20,793
God-damned it! Speak!

2059
01:43:20,994 --> 01:43:22,689
To the east, to the east!

2060
01:43:23,564 --> 01:43:26,556
Come back! You mustn't go that way!

2061
