2067
01:43:57,864 --> 01:43:59,058
Don't worry.

2068
01:43:59,967 --> 01:44:01,400
I really am "Pocky" Zhang.

2069
01:44:02,402 --> 01:44:04,632
Pocky!

2070
01:44:04,871 --> 01:44:06,896
My ass...

2071
