2121
01:48:10,684 --> 01:48:12,151
They're a bunch of clowns!

2122
01:48:12,352 --> 01:48:14,320
We simply want them... dead!

2123
01:48:14,654 --> 01:48:15,916
He has sworn publicly,

2124
01:48:16,990 --> 01:48:18,855
